664
01:36:21.384 --> 01:36:23.722
Kom igen. Kom igen.

665
01:38:45.041 --> 01:38:46.279
Min vän...

666
01:38:47.488 --> 01:38:49.032
Jag hittade henne.

667
01:38:51.125 --> 01:38:52.133
Jag hittade henne.

